{"tid":1311894,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[文宣]我諗到條絕世好橋","createTime":"2019-07-13T11:21:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-13T12:19:58.000Z","uid":225916,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"dacc797e6579cdc3a22bd58658394a1e9d8a8d18","tid":1311894,"uid":225916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T11:21:44.000Z","msg":"有鑑於好多巴打話:<br />\n我老豆都有上連登、我老豆上連登後開始反共&hellip;等等<br />\n<br />\n所以得出一個結論就係:<br />\n思想改變佢哋 俾佢哋接收更多元化資訊<br />\n<br />\n佢哋成為藍絲都係因為俾人洗腦<br />\n所以我哋要反洗腦式 叫佢哋上連登<br />\n吸收我哋哩邊嘅資訊 思想改造佢哋<br />\n<br />\n唔該咁多位幫手推post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d6573a7099a0cd59ca2cb94376ad589c3c19d21","tid":1311894,"uid":225916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T11:22:49.000Z","msg":"一齊叫佢哋上連登<br />\n將連登搬到佢哋前面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n等佢哋加入連登討論區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fae20126567932b1fd2d755597a71cc52429386","tid":1311894,"uid":225916,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T11:24:34.000Z","msg":"全力呼籲身邊人上連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最簡單直接方法:將連登post share出去<br />\n然後同佢講 其實連登好多嘢睇架"},{"pid":"dd330025a1e40cc1efd1d3154f1d3eb8f352f720","tid":1311894,"uid":225916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T11:28:15.000Z","msg":"幫手推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d743db400db5a1686520a1776a4bf9ebdc924c61","tid":1311894,"uid":225916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T11:36:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cb03daa86887c1bf3bee241b32eb4e50c70f5232","tid":1311894,"uid":225916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T11:43:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dd01937a03bc61e55186f3acd63751aa6cfb9154","tid":1311894,"uid":225916,"like":0,"dis